Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.34,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't shoot Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something like this could kill her,\Nwe wouldn't have this problem, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch! We're off the main road!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way leads to the ocean.\NIt's a dead end ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a payoff for being religious.\NAll survivors, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're safe, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still unconscious... peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world\Nis that woman made of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. Hey, what happened to\Nthat damn bitch? Is she dead? Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be glad to know\Nthat she's alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just delightful.\NMore than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. I'm about to become\Nas red as a tail light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens,\Nit's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to warn you even if\NI'm about to give you extra assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shell she used\Nto blow me away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is gonna cost her more than\Nanything she could stick up her ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go beat that into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon draw, Senorita.\NOr are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no need\Nto use filthy words and be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you could not\Ndefeat me with skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you pointed a gun at the\Nyoung master and kidnapped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. Watch out for stray bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see either of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww... Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She managed to get a bullet into\Nthe great Revy. Who is that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you could've had\Na good upbringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?\NTell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no surprise that's the smell\Nyou have on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stench of gutter-mud\Nstuck to your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more reason\Nwhy we'll have to settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... What should we do now?\NMaybe we should get outta this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, impossible. We'd never make it\Nno matter how many lives we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not about to go anywhere\Nnear that fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an end to every beginning.\NThey'll settle things eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!!\NRoberta!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you lose to that woman!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gunfire is getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This bitch! I'm gonna kill her!{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm gonna kill her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're going to hell!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you\Ncall it quits now, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to gain\Nfrom fighting anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste your energy,\NTwo Hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.\NI'm gonna kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something\Ninteresting, Miss Maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, at Hotel Moscow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...had intended to start a war...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...against the Manisarela Cartel\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking care\Nof them was my job...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you saved me\Nthe trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, their headquarters in\NVenezuela should be in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, all of the problems\Nhave been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The case of Garcia being kidnapped\Nhas also been dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no reason to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are no doubt the three\Nmost terrifying women in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels like Ground Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand me.\NI'm not making a request. It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are these guys?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They don't seem like{\i0}\N{\i1}the usual Russian mafia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Military uniforms?{\i0}\N{\i1}Are they soldiers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Roberta!\NAs you can see, I'm not hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?\NLet's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna see\Nyou with a gun anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree, kid. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what does the Bloodhound think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloodhound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. So you don't know? She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet, bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't some servant\Nwho looks good walking the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Bloodhound of Florencia".\NRosarita Cisneros.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trained as an assassin in Cuba,\Nshe's a former F.A.R.C. guerrilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's wanted internationally for\Nmultiple kidnappings and murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's suspected\Nof being involved with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the bombing of the\NU. S. embassy in Tegucigalpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a real hardcore terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I had no intention of\Ndeceiving you, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, young master.\NThere are things in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you're better off not knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I believed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the morning of a revolution that\Nwould bring justice to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason,\NI became a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my pursuit of the ideal,\NI killed in every place imaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Politicians, entrepreneurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...anti-revolutionists,\Nelection management members.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even killed women\Nand children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying many nights with blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and facing many\Ncold hearted mornings...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what I realized in the end was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I was no revolutionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was nothing but a guard dog for\Nthe mafia and their cocaine fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it ironic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The revolutionists joined forces\Nwith the cartels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying that a revolution\Nwould not happen solely on ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As they blurted out those words,\Nthey sold their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who took me in then was\Nmy deceased father's friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...none other than your father,\NMaster Diego Lovelace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allowing your kidnapping to happen\Nwas negligence on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not have any other\Nway to save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...than becoming my old,\Nsteel self that I once abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloodhound.\NGuard dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only way that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being called a dog,\Ncould repay you with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call yourself a dog, Roberta!\NYou're my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're family, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that,\Nabout being a dog! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know any Bloodhound!\NShe probably died somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Rosarita woman has probably\Ngone to some unknown...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...far away place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...burdened with her sins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's got nothing\Nto do with you, Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one here\Nis my Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, okay?\NLet's go back to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young master.\NBoys should not cry so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad that's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're all delighted with\Nthis teary-eyed happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who the hell is gonna close up\Nthis tunnel in my shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just\Nput up with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Sis.\NThat stinks, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our world,\Nsettling things is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that perfectly well, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have them go at each other\Nin a fistfight until they're satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no prize at stake,\Nso no one's likely to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you lose to that woman!\NYou're strong, Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to continue\Nas long as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shoelace is untied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got one in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice to be so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Roberta!\NDon't lose to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you betting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting two\Non Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going with three on Roberta.\NHow about you, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait a minute!\NWe should be stopping them! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta make\Nthem stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too barbaric, and you guys\Nare crazy not to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absurd to have two girls\Ngoing at it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you go\Nand stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Well...\N- Then go and stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could maybe, you know,\Nlike, sit back and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...praise each other's\Ncombative spirit as you gaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...at the rising sun together?\N- Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand. I'll do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just won't give up.\NThis is getting boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you die already?\NDamned four-eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:19:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too...\Njust let me knock you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young master.\NI am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the last one standing.\NSo it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What a terrible face.\N- She's unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?\NCome on, hang onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna hand, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta is a maid at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't need anyone else's help.\NI will be sure to take her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wonderful future\Nhead of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Comrade Sergeant.\N- Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treat her wounds,\Nthen take them to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If any remaining cartel members\Nattempt an assault, dispose of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young master.\NI have one favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please go\Nand pick up my glasses for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Those are fake,\Naren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need those glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to continue being\Nyour Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's morning, Revy!\NWake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely no sign of waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gonna take time to recover.\NOh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who were those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balalaika and the Russian mafia guys.\NThey were like the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are ex-military.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were either in the paratroopers\Nor the Special Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her immediate subordinates\Nhad enough training...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to carry out World War III.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afghan vets with an insane amount\Nof experience and skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With her as the brains, every one\Nof them acted as a killing machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And eventually they returned from\Nthat hell of hot sand and slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone's feet are covered{\i0}\N{\i1}with mud from the gutter.{\i0}
